These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, comedy, fantasy, superhero, romance, western
 1. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching superhero movies##7
 3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching adventure movies##7
 4. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
 5. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 6. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 8. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching western movies##7
 9. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | adventure | crime | comedy | fantasy | romance | western |

