.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: tennis, basketball, rugby, surfing, golf, badminton, handball
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person who's sport is handball is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Sport   | surfing | basketball | badminton | handball | rugby | tennis | golf |

