.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, hiking, sudoku, camping, fishing, board-games, collecting
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is hiking##7
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | fishing | board-games | camping | collecting | singing | sudoku | hiking |

