.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, water, lemonade, mirinda, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking tea##7
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking tea##7
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking lemonade##7
 6. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person drinking lemonade##8
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea | lemonade | hot-chocolate | mirinda | tea | almond-milk |

