 3. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking tea##7
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking water##2
10. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
